{"tid":1912780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日女神級易容變TWICE Mina　素顏震驚網民：這化妝技術太強了！","createTime":"2020-03-06T10:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T11:15:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"2401122e4c1bc76833f9419d461fa9992b4e99a9","tid":1912780,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"古語有云，「世界上沒有醜女人，只有懶女人」。當今世上，有各種形形色色的化妝品，只要肯下苦功練習，任你外表平凡也可以變偶像神顏！<br />\n<br />\n近日日本有位女生分享自己的化妝前後對比，由普通女生變身成人氣韓國偶像組合TWICE的Mina，令不少網民大為震驚！<br />\n<br />\n這位女生叫Rina，近日於個人Twitter自嘲醜得像隻老鼠，靠努力練習不同化妝技巧，總算能讓自己由醜小鴨變天鵝。<br />\n<br />\n她亦於YouTube分享化妝過程及心得，不少網民表示超震驚，沒想到化妝後竟與TWICE Mina相似度達9成，而且素顏差距也不少，簡直就像易容一樣！<br />\n<br />\nRina熱愛韓國偶像文化，除了當YouTuber外，她還經營叫「Like A Miracle」的飾品店，專門搜羅偶像們佩戴過的飾品。"},{"pid":"09461991e84b9327cabda33b671eedd5ce8ccdf7","tid":1912780,"uid":16659,"like":38,"dislike":42,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESRLumZUcAAGPKi?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESRLumZUcAAGPKi%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=c2631b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESRLumXUMAApc4_?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESRLumXUMAApc4_%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=50bda443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESRLumcU8AADOHx?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESRLumcU8AADOHx%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=e51b17b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESRLupSUwAEHgPa?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESRLupSUwAEHgPa%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=00714ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2649c9cf65a1307a4bb7bab95e916ca8effa65d6","ti